1334 static void MmwDemo_mboxReadTask(UArg arg0, UArg arg1)
1335 {
1336  MmwDemo_message message;
1337  int32_t retVal = 0;
1338  uint32_t totalPacketLen;
1339  uint32_t numPaddingBytes;
1340  uint32_t itemIdx;
1341 
1342  /* wait for new message and process all the messages received from the peer */
1343  while(1)
1344  {
1345  Semaphore_pend(gMmwMssMCB.mboxSemHandle, BIOS_WAIT_FOREVER);
1346 
1347  /* Read the message from the peer mailbox: We are not trying to protect the read
1348  * from the peer mailbox because this is only being invoked from a single thread */
1349  retVal = Mailbox_read(gMmwMssMCB.peerMailbox, (uint8_t*)&message, sizeof(MmwDemo_message));
1350  if (retVal < 0)
1351  {
1352  /* Error: Unable to read the message. Setup the error code and return values */
1353  System_printf ("Error: Mailbox read failed [Error code %d]\n", retVal);
1354  }
1355  else if (retVal == 0)
1356  {
1357  /* We are done: There are no messages available from the peer execution domain. */
1358  continue;
1359  }
1360  else
1361  {
1362  /* Flush out the contents of the mailbox to indicate that we are done with the message. This will
1363  * allow us to receive another message in the mailbox while we process the received message. */
1364  Mailbox_readFlush (gMmwMssMCB.peerMailbox);
1365 
1366  /* Process the received message: */
1367  switch (message.type)
1368  {
1369  case MMWDEMO_DSS2MSS_DETOBJ_READY:
1370  /* Got detetced objectes , shipped out through UART */
1371  /* Send header */
1372  totalPacketLen = sizeof(MmwDemo_output_message_header);
1373  UART_writePolling (gMmwMssMCB.loggingUartHandle,
1374  (uint8_t*)&message.body.detObj.header,
1375  sizeof(MmwDemo_output_message_header));
1376 
1377  /* Send TLVs */
1378  for (itemIdx = 0; itemIdx < message.body.detObj.header.numTLVs; itemIdx++)
1379  {
1380  UART_writePolling (gMmwMssMCB.loggingUartHandle,
1381  (uint8_t*)&message.body.detObj.tlv[itemIdx],
1382  sizeof(MmwDemo_output_message_tl));
1383  UART_writePolling (gMmwMssMCB.loggingUartHandle,
1384  (uint8_t*)SOC_translateAddress(message.body.detObj.tlv[itemIdx].address,
1385  SOC_TranslateAddr_Dir_FROM_OTHER_CPU,NULL),
1386  message.body.detObj.tlv[itemIdx].length);
1387  totalPacketLen += sizeof(MmwDemo_output_message_tl) + message.body.detObj.tlv[itemIdx].length;
1388  }
1389 
1390  /* Send padding to make total packet length multiple of MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN */
1391  numPaddingBytes = MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN - (totalPacketLen & (MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN-1));
1392  if (numPaddingBytes<MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN)
1393  {
1394  uint8_t padding[MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN];
1395  /*DEBUG:*/ memset(&padding, 0xf, MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN);
1396  UART_writePolling (gMmwMssMCB.loggingUartHandle,
1397  padding,
1398  numPaddingBytes);
1399  }
1400 
1401  /* Send a message to MSS to log the output data */
1402  memset((void *)&message, 0, sizeof(MmwDemo_message));
1403 
1404  message.type = MMWDEMO_MSS2DSS_DETOBJ_SHIPPED;
1405 
1406  if (MmwDemo_mboxWrite(&message) != 0)
1407  {
1408  System_printf ("Error: Mailbox send message id=%d failed \n", message.type);
1409  }
1410 
1411  break;
1412  case MMWDEMO_DSS2MSS_STOPDONE:
1413  /* Post event that stop is done */
1414  gMmwMssMCB.stats.dssSensorStop++;
1415  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_STOP_COMPLETED_EVT);
1416  break;
1417  case MMWDEMO_DSS2MSS_ASSERT_INFO:
1418  /* Send the received DSS assert info through CLI */
1419  CLI_write ("DSS Exception: %s, line %d.\n", message.body.assertInfo.file,
1420  message.body.assertInfo.line);
1421  break;
1422  case MMWDEMO_DSS2MSS_ISR_INFO_ADDRESS:
1423  gMmwMssMCB.dss2mssIsrInfoAddress =
1424  SOC_translateAddress(message.body.dss2mssISRinfoAddress,
1425  SOC_TranslateAddr_Dir_FROM_OTHER_CPU, NULL);
1426  MmwDemo_installDss2MssExceptionSignallingISR();
1427  break;
1428  case MMWDEMO_DSS2MSS_MEASUREMENT_INFO:
1429  /* Send the received DSS calibration info through CLI */
1430  CLI_write ("compRangeBiasAndRxChanPhase");
1431  CLI_write (" %.7f", message.body.compRxChanCfg.rangeBias);
1432  int32_t i;
1433  for (i = 0; i < SYS_COMMON_NUM_TX_ANTENNAS*SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL; i++)
1434  {
1435  CLI_write (" %.5f", (float) message.body.compRxChanCfg.rxChPhaseComp[i].real/32768.);
1436  CLI_write (" %.5f", (float) message.body.compRxChanCfg.rxChPhaseComp[i].imag/32768.);
1437  }
1438  CLI_write ("\n");
1439  break;
1440  default:
1441  {
1442  /* Message not support */
1443  System_printf ("Error: unsupport Mailbox message id=%d\n", message.type);
1444  break;
1445  }
1446  }
1447  }
1448  }
1449 }

1961 void MmwDemo_mssCtrlPathTask(UArg arg0, UArg arg1)
1962 {
1963  UInt event;
1964 
1965  /**********************************************************************
1966  * Setup the PINMUX:
1967  * - GPIO Input : Configure pin J13 as GPIO_1 input
1968  * - GPIO Output: Configure pin K13 as GPIO_2 output
1969  **********************************************************************/
1970  Pinmux_Set_OverrideCtrl(SOC_XWR16XX_PINJ13_PADAC, PINMUX_OUTEN_RETAIN_HW_CTRL, PINMUX_INPEN_RETAIN_HW_CTRL);
1971  Pinmux_Set_FuncSel(SOC_XWR16XX_PINJ13_PADAC, SOC_XWR16XX_PINJ13_PADAC_GPIO_1);
1972  Pinmux_Set_OverrideCtrl(SOC_XWR16XX_PINK13_PADAZ, PINMUX_OUTEN_RETAIN_HW_CTRL, PINMUX_INPEN_RETAIN_HW_CTRL);
1973  Pinmux_Set_FuncSel(SOC_XWR16XX_PINK13_PADAZ, SOC_XWR16XX_PINK13_PADAZ_GPIO_2);
1974 
1975  /**********************************************************************
1976  * Setup the SW1 switch on the EVM connected to GPIO_1
1977  * - This is used as an input
1978  * - Enable interrupt to be notified on a switch press
1979  **********************************************************************/
1980  GPIO_setConfig (SOC_XWR16XX_GPIO_1, GPIO_CFG_INPUT | GPIO_CFG_IN_INT_RISING | GPIO_CFG_IN_INT_LOW);
1981  GPIO_setCallback (SOC_XWR16XX_GPIO_1, MmwDemo_switchPressFxn);
1982  GPIO_enableInt (SOC_XWR16XX_GPIO_1);
1983 
1984  /**********************************************************************
1985  * Setup the DS3 LED on the EVM connected to GPIO_2
1986  **********************************************************************/
1987  GPIO_setConfig (SOC_XWR16XX_GPIO_2, GPIO_CFG_OUTPUT);
1988 
1989  /* Data Path management task Main loop */
1990  while (1)
1991  {
1992  event = Event_pend(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandle,
1993  Event_Id_NONE,
1994  MMWDEMO_CLI_EVENTS | MMWDEMO_BSS_FAULT_EVENTS |
1995  MMWDEMO_DSS_EXCEPTION_EVENTS,
1996  BIOS_WAIT_FOREVER);
1997 
1998  /************************************************************************
1999  * CLI event:: SensorStart
2000  ************************************************************************/
2001 
2002  if(event & MMWDEMO_CLI_SENSORSTART_EVT)
2003  {
2004  System_printf ("Debug: MMWDemoMSS Received CLI sensorStart Event\n");
2005 
2006  /* Setup the data path: */
2007  if(gMmwMssMCB.isSensorStarted==false)
2008  {
2009  if (MmwDemo_mssDataPathConfig () < 0) {
2010  /* Post start failed event; error printing is done in function above */
2011  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_START_FAILED_EVT);
2012  continue;
2013  }
2014  else
2015  {
2016  /* start complete event is posted via DSS */
2017  }
2018  }
2019  else
2020  {
2021  /* Post start complete event as this is just a duplicate command */
2022  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_START_COMPLETED_EVT);
2023  continue;
2024  }
2025  }
2026 
2027  /************************************************************************
2028  * CLI event:: SensorStop
2029  ************************************************************************/
2030  if(event & MMWDEMO_CLI_SENSORSTOP_EVT)
2031  {
2032  if(gMmwMssMCB.isSensorStarted==true)
2033  {
2034  if (MmwDemo_mssDataPathStop () < 0) {
2035  /* Do we need stop fail event? */
2036  DebugP_assert(0);
2037  }
2038  else
2039  {
2040  /* DSS will post the stop completed event */
2041  }
2042  }
2043  else
2044  {
2045  /* Post data path stop complete event on behalf on Datapath in case sensor is already in stop state */
2046  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_STOP_COMPLETED_EVT);
2047  }
2048 
2049  /* In all cases send MSS stop complete */
2050  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_MSS_STOP_COMPLETED_EVT);
2051  }
2052 
2053  /************************************************************************
2054  * CLI event:: Framestart
2055  ************************************************************************/
2056  if(event & MMWDEMO_CLI_FRAMESTART_EVT)
2057  {
2058  /* error printing happens inside this function */
2059  if(gMmwMssMCB.isSensorStarted==false)
2060  {
2061  if (MmwDemo_mssDataPathStart () < 0) {
2062  /* Post start failed event; error printing is done in function above */
2063  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_START_FAILED_EVT);
2064  continue;
2065  }
2066  }
2067 
2068  /* Post event to start is done */
2069  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_START_COMPLETED_EVT);
2070  }
2071 
2072  /************************************************************************
2073  * BSS event:: CPU fault
2074  ************************************************************************/
2075  if(event & MMWDEMO_BSS_CPUFAULT_EVT)
2076  {
2077  MmwDemo_mssAssert(0);
2078  break;
2079  }
2080 
2081  /************************************************************************
2082  * BSS event:: ESM fault
2083  ************************************************************************/
2084  if(event & MMWDEMO_BSS_ESMFAULT_EVT)
2085  {
2086  MmwDemo_mssAssert(0);
2087  break;
2088  }
2089 
2090  /************************************************************************
2091  * BSS event:: Analog fault
2092  ************************************************************************/
2093  if (event & MMWDEMO_BSS_ANALOGFAULT_EVT)
2094  {
2095  MmwDemo_mssAssert(0);
2096  break;
2097  }
2098 
2099  if(event & MMWDEMO_DSS_CHIRP_PROC_DEADLINE_MISS_EVT)
2100  {
2101  CLI_write ("DSS Chirp Processing Deadline Miss Exception.\n");
2102  DebugP_assert(0);
2103  break;
2104  }
2105 
2106  if(event & MMWDEMO_DSS_FRAME_PROC_DEADLINE_MISS_EVT)
2107  {
2108  CLI_write ("DSS Frame Processing Deadline Miss Exception.\n");
2109  DebugP_assert(0);
2110  break;
2111  }
2112  }
2113 
2114  System_printf("Debug: MMWDemoDSS Data path exit\n");
2115 }
